emuInput.TitMainTitle: Winners of high school cake baking contest, from left: Peggy Daniels, Clara Tucciaione, Norma Lee, James Gay, Elaine Butler, and Betty Smith posed in front of Westinghouse home appliance display in Syria Mosque for the 1958 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 5, 1958, pg. 3 reads: "1. High School Home EC Students thrilled at visiting the Home Show, as shown by 1. Winners of the high school cake-baking contest, left to right, Peggy Daniels, Fifth Avenue High School, first prize; Clara Tucciaione, Westinghouse High School, second prize; Norma Lee, Westinghouse High School, fifth prize; James Gay, Peabody High School, third prize, and Elaine Butler and Betty Smith, Herron Hill Junior High School, fourth prize..."
